<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('partials/header') %>
<body>
<%- include('partials/navbar') %>

<div id="carouselFS" class="carousel slide wraprafa" data-ride="carousel" Style="box-shadow:0.1px 10px 12px #1C2331">
  <ol class="carousel-indicators">
    <li data-target="#carouselFS" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
    <li data-target="#carouselFS" data-slide-to="1"></li>
    <li data-target="#carouselFS" data-slide-to="2"></li>
  </ol>
  <div class="carousel-inner">
    <div class="carousel-item active">
	  <div class="slidetext">
        <h3>Who are we?</h3>
        <p>A group of students working for a University project application that will help locate free parking spots for Aberdeen City.</p>
      </div>
      <img class="d-block w-100" src="Images\whoarewe.jpg" alt="First slide">
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
	  <div class="slidetext">
        <h3>Philosophy</h3>
        <p>If you pay road tax, you deserve free parking. Cars are not a luxury anymore, they are a necessity and so is free parking.</p>
      </div>
      <img class="d-block w-100" src="Images\philosophy.jpg" alt="Second slide">
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
	  <div class="slidetext">
        <h3>Goals</h3>
        <p>To be the most complete application for free parking in Aberdeen city.</p>
      </div>
      <img class="d-block w-100" src="Images\goals.jpg" alt="Third slide">
    </div>
  </div>
  <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselFS" role="button" data-slide="prev">
    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
  </a>
  <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselFS" role="button" data-slide="next">
    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
  </a>
</div>
</div>
<div id="ourMission" class="container-fluid wraprafa" style="background:#253241 box-shadow:0.1px 10px 12px #1C2331">
  <h2 style="color:white; text-align:center">Our mission</h2>
  <p style="color:white; text-align:center"><br>Parking is one of the most difficult and dysfunctional parts of modern city life – and that’s no surprise, as it’s barely changed for decades. Over 23% of car journeys involve some kind of parking pain – that’s 190 million trips a month – with drivers suffering from both uncertainty (availability, prices, restrictions) and inconvenience (full car parks, slow payments, unfair fines) on a daily basis. Yet we have the technology to make parking function seamlessly – and so much space is lying underutilised. There has to be a better system… At FindSpot, we are on a mission to make parking easy. Findspot is dedicated to solving the parking problem by cracking both sides of the market – making parking easy and efficient for everyone.<br><br><br></p>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid wraprafa" style="background:#f2f2f2">
<div class="box">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-lg-12">
			<h2 class="intro-text text-left" style="color:black"><br>Contact Us</h2>
			<form>
				<div class="row">
					<div class="form-group col-lg-4">
						<label>Name*</label>
						<input type="text" class="form-control">
					</div>
					<div class="form-group col-lg-4">
						<label>Email*</label>
						<input type="email" class="form-control">
					</div>
					<div class="form-group col-lg-4">
						<label>Phone Number*</label>
						<input type="tel" class="form-control">
					</div>
					<div class="form-group col-lg-12">
						<label>Message</label>
						<textarea class="form-control" rows="6"></textarea>
					</div>
					<div class="form-group col-lg-12">
						<input type="hidden" name="save" value="contact">
						<button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">Submit</button>
					</div>

				</div>
			</form>
	</div>
	</div>
	</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
